### Java

```java

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Test {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		// TODO Auto-generated method stub

		Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);

		while (true) {

			String s = sc.nextLine();
			if (s.length() == 0) {
				break;
			}
			System.out.println(s);

		}

		System.out.println("end");

	}

}


```
